data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful 2-story home that offers the enjoyment of a quiet corner lot with covered patio, built in grill and fire pit, for that cool, shady summer evening gatherings. Home appraised for $735,000 in July 2022, This was before Full Chef Kitchen remodel along with New Iron Stair Railings. 
Here are some favorite interior features:
- Brand New Chef Kitchen
- The open main floor living area provides ample opportunities to host large gatherings
- Perfectly tucked away on the main floor is a Full bedroom and Full bath that provides added convenience
- Upstairs offers an expansive primary en-suite with a large walk-in closet, a sizable loft, 2 additional bedrooms with a full bath as well as the centrally located laundry room
- Fully Finished Basement that offers an additional Family Room, 2 Bedrooms, Full Bathroom, with a Office Nook, and Kitchenette
